{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},